query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(ci rt an) NoMergeJoin(an ci rt mc) NoHashJoin(an ci mc rt cn) NoMergeJoin(an ci cn mc rt t) NoHashJoin(an ci cn mc mi rt t chn) NoMergeJoin(an chn ci cn mc mi rt t n) NoMergeJoin(an chn ci cn mc mi n rt t it) */ select min(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
min(t.title) AS jap_engl_voiced_movie
from role_type AS rt
inner join cast_info AS ci
on rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress' AND ci.note IN ('(executive producer)',
'(voice)',
'(uncredited)',
'(as Claire) (credit only)')
inner join aka_name AS an
on ci.person_id = an.person_id
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
inner join company_name AS cn
on cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2006
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
inner join char_name AS chn
on chn.id = ci.person_role_id
inner join name AS n
on n.id = an.person_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f'
inner join info_type AS it
on it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates';
